drizzle/

# Cardmaker generated content (assets + per-card pages) — created from
# client/ + shared/ by generateAssets.ts. Every directory under cardmaker/
# is generated EXCEPT the negated source dirs; when adding a new source
# directory there, negate it here too. #
sites/cardmaker/assets/
sites/cardmaker/*/
!sites/cardmaker/search/
